     H            Y.
     F** UTLR04 ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY - GET PF BY LF                   *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)                                 *
     F*           01/27/2016                               *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR04'
     F*                    PARM           $FILE  10
     F*                    PARM           $PF    10
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $FILE  : 10A LF
     F*  OUT $PF    : 10A PF
     F*      $RTN   :  1A RETURN CODE (BLANK/*)
     F******************************************************
     FVVVPPA1 IF  E           K        DISK
     FVVVPLA1 IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     E                    DAT        10  1
     I            DS
     I                                        1  10 @FILE
     I                                        4   4 @P4
     I                                        5   5 @P5
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C                     EXSR @INIT
      *
     C           $FILE     CHAINVVVPPA1              90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C           $FILE     CHAINVVVPLA1              91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C           @P4       IFEQ 'W'
     C           @P5       ANDEQ'P'
     C           @P4       OREQ 'P'
     C           @P5       ANDEQ'P'
     C                     MOVEL$FILE     VVRFI
     C                     GOTO @OK
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     GOTO @END
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           @OK       TAG
     C                     MOVELVVRFI     $PF
     C                     GOTO @END
      *
     C           @END      TAG
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *=============================================================
      *                    INITIAL PROCESS
      *=============================================================
     C           @INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $FILE  10
     C                     PARM           $PF    10
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C                     MOVEL$FILE     @FILE
     C                     CLEAR$PF
     C                     CLEAR$RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
